dc_title_s: Annual Small Area Population and Household Estimates, Twin Cities Metropolitan Area: Metro Twin Cities, Minnesota
dc_description_s: This dataset consists of housing unit, household, and population estimates for census tracts and Transportation Analysis Zones (TAZs) in the Twin Cities Region. These data provide a more precise and timely picture of current conditions than the American Community Survey, another source of small area data. It may be possible to calculate estimates for other small areas upon request; contact Research@metc.state.mn.us for more information.
